programme.title: NFL - Greatest Games
programme.desc: Miami Dolphins v San Diego Chargers. A review of the AFC Championship Game played in 1982, which came to be known as the `epic in Miami'. The Chargers started the first quarter in scintillating form, and raced to a 24-0 lead that appeared to have settled the contest in their favour early on. However, The Dolphins battled back in the second quarter, scoring 17 unanswered points to narrow the margin, and at the end of the fourth quarter the teams were tied at 38-38. Despite the extreme heat and humidity, and with many players suffering the effects of dehydration, it took a further 14 minutes of overtime before San Diego kicked a winning field goal to eventually claim a 41-28 victory, and progress to the Super Bowl.(n)

V ligi, ki je bila ustanovljena 6. junija 1946 v New Yorku, nastopa 30 ekip, ena od teh je kanadska. S 17 naslovi za najuspešnejšo ekipo tekmovanja v zgodovini velja Boston Celtics, v zadnjem letu pa so naslov osvojili košarkarji Golden Stata, ki so bili v finalu močnejši od Clevelanda LeBrona Jamesa.

programme.title: Spanish league: Villarreal - Espanyol
programme.desc: Španska nogometna liga, bolj poznana pod vzdevkom La Liga, je najelitnejše nogometno tekmovanje v Španiji. Ustanovljena je bila leta 1929. V ligi nastopa 20 klubov. Z naskokom najuspešnejša kluba sta madridski Real in Barcelona. Zadnji naslov je romal v roke Kataloncem.

programme.title: Turška liga: Alanyaspor - Galatasaray

programme.title: Portugal liga: Vitoria Guimaraes - Porto
programme.desc: Nekoč Primeira Liga, danes Liga NOS je najelitnejše nogometno tekmovanje na Portugalskem.
